{"type": "article", "id": 22693, "title": "Néit 可压缩旅行箱", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-23T07:30:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 82, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702135505ZIgkT6q2o34yl5hW.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">英国设计团队 Néit 推出了一款可折叠的行李箱，不用的时候就将行李箱两侧向内翻折，使原有的立体空间完全压缩成一个平面，就像衣服一样完全可以挂在晾衣杆上，大大节省占用的空间。这个旅行箱采用聚碳酸酯（PC）材料，表面有波浪花紋来增加强度，产品目前在众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/neit/neit-revolutionary-smart-collapsible-hard-case-lug\">这里是众筹链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135459inFVhM3HsU92ezRf.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66568483\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135459ZW4H6tNKiDekE9j0.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021355020eBaRvwt9oukhcXp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61230769\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702135502jVbFHrIm2OSJaD1l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.96153846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213550450Q1ZpE7WIVtGmUT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72307692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}